pr_body:
```smalltalk
| boxPlot1 toothGrowth |
toothGrowth := AIDatasets loadToothGrowth.
boxPlot1 := RSViolinPlot dataFrame: toothGrowth x: #dose y: #len.
boxPlot1 color: Color purple translucent.
"boxPlot1 bandwidth: 2."
^ boxPlot1 open
```
